---
import heroImg from '../assets/hero-holographic.png';
---
<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
    <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left">
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
        E se a sua empresa pudesse sentir?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
        A Aurora é o Sistema Operacional de IA que conecta, aprende e atua proativamente para transformar o seu negócio.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <a href="/demo" class="px-6 py-3 bg-aurora-accent text-white rounded-xl shadow-soft hover:opacity-90 transition">Ver Demo</a>
        <a href="/contato" class="px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Falar com Vendas</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 relative">
      <img src={heroImg} alt="Rosto holográfico Aurora" class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto drop-shadow-2xl rounded-2xl" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
